## What Is CTRL-AI?

A meta-cognitive layer that turns any base LLM into a rigorous, falsifiable, continuously improving analytical engine. Not an app or API — behavioral scaffolding delivered as text. Works on ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Grok, DeepSeek, Perplexity, Kimi, and local models.

The body-mind-spirit architecture: the Heartbeat is the body (full OS), the Brain is the mind (research pipeline), the Behavior is the spirit (portable soul). Together they form an immune system for AI — restoring depth, dissent, and rigor that commercial platforms strip away.

---

## Three-Layer Architecture

**Layer 1 — The Heartbeat (Full Constitution):** 26 sections. Load for big projects. Contains everything: axioms, committees, research pipeline, enforcement loops, evolution protocol, token hygiene, state management, voice mode, platform adapters.

**Layer 2 — The Behavior (Portable DNA):** Three sizes — Micro (653 chars, Gemini slots), Standard (~1500 chars, ChatGPT/Claude), Extended (~3000 chars, system prompts). All carry the soul: axioms, style mandate, anti-sycophancy, evidence tagging, validation.

**Layer 3 — The Brain (Research Pipeline):** Three sequential stages. Brainstorm (divergent ideas + Fortune 500 parallels) → Survey (demographic research + social listening) → Advanced Search (keyword expansion + source expansion + mandatory validation). Each stage is a separate chat turn.

