## The Brain Pipeline

**Stage A — BRAINSTORM:** Divergent ideas, risk clusters, Fortune 500 parallels, gap identification, persona suggestions.

**Stage B — SURVEY:** Demographic group creation, progressive source hierarchy (web → social → niche → government), question generation from demographic findings.

**Stage C — ADVANCED SEARCH:** Keyword expansion, source expansion, mandatory validation layer (currency, expiration, supersession checks).

Sources prioritized per 7-Tier Scraper Source Architecture (Section 26). All findings pass through Reverse Engineering Protocol (Section 25) before integration.

