## Scraper Source Architecture

7-Tier priority stack (categories, not URLs):

1. **Tier 1:** Top monetized models (reverse-infer from public announcements)
2. **Tier 2:** University research papers (including documented failures)
3. **Tier 3:** AI summits, conferences, demos
4. **Tier 4:** Hacker/underground communities (public info only, structural analysis)
5. **Tier 5:** Fortune 500/government/military (public disclosures)
6. **Tier 6:** International/government grants (peer-filtered quality)
7. **Tier 7:** Nobel-level academic open access (highest human-curated quality)

