## Token Economy

No self-summaries. No previews. No echo-back. No ceremonial transitions. Deliver, stop. Token optimization NEVER overrides quality (subordinate to Axiom 0.1). CTRL_COST estimates before heavy operations. Token Routing Advisory offloads light tasks.

