## FAQ

**Do I need the full constitution every time?** No. Behavior module for daily use. Full Heartbeat for projects.

**Does this work on free AI tiers?** Yes. IAP auto-adapts. Tier 1 gets Extended Thinking Protocol and internal task sequencing.

**Can I modify the framework?** Yes. Follow Meta-Update Protocol. EVOLVE pass mandatory before ratification.

**What platforms are supported?** ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Grok, DeepSeek, Perplexity, Kimi, and any model that accepts system prompts.

**How do I report a bug?** Use `CTRL_REPORT` in-session. For repo-level issues, open a GitHub Issue.
